<plot>A sprawling turn of the century academy, a billboard charts band fueled by deceit, and an art gallery that comes to life with graphic paintings revealing each character dying a horrible death that begins to hint at the real terror lurking behind every one of us. "13 Seconds" boldly mixes "The Shining"-like chills with the rapid action pacing of "The Terminator" which challenges the viewer to solve its mystery. It is a compelling thriller that devillishly destroys one cliche after another while speeding towards a shocking, surprise ending that comes complete with crawlspace chases, seances, a malevolent art gallery, and an unstoppable evil older than time itself.</plot><plot>A sprawling turn of the century academy, a billboard charts band fueled by deceit, and an art gallery that comes to life with graphic paintings revealing each character dying a horrible death that begins to hint at the real terror lurking behind every one of us. "13 Seconds" boldly mixes "The Shining"-like chills with the rapid action pacing of "The Terminator" which challenges the viewer to solve its mystery. It is a compelling thriller that devillishly destroys one cliche after another while speeding towards a shocking, surprise ending that comes complete with crawlspace chases, seances, a malevolent art gallery, and an unstoppable evil older than time itself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?002259</url></doc>
